    "Remote MCP is not mainly a convenience problem. The production checklist is principal model, scope boundaries, transport and middleware boundaries, tenant isolation, governors, recovery, and auditability.",
  url: "https://rhumb.dev/blog/remote-mcp-production-readiness-checklist",
